quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  20,52,(Musa) aravuga ati “Ubumenyi bwabyo buri mu gitabo kwa Nyagasani wanjye. Nyagasani wanjye ntajya yibeshya cyangwa ngo yibagirwe.”
  20,53,"Ni We wabagiriye isi nk’isaso, anabashyiriramo amayira menshi ndetse anabamanurira amazi mu kirere (imvura), nuko tuyameresha ibimera by’amoko atandukanye"
  20,54,Ngaho nimurye (muri ibyo bimera) munabiragiremo amatungo yanyu. Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso (bigaragaza ubushobozi bwa Allah) ku banyabwenge
  20,55,"Twabaremye tubakomoye mu gitaka, ni na cyo tubasubizamo (igihe mwapfuye), ndetse ni na cyo tuzongera kubavanamo ku yindi nshuro (igihe cyo kuzurwa)"
  20,56,"Mu by’ukuri (Farawo) twamweretse ibitangaza byacu byose, ariko yarabihinyuye yanga no kwemera"
  20,57,"(Farawo) aravuga ati “Ese wazanywe no kutwirukana mu gihugu cyacu ukoresheje uburozi bwawe, yewe Musa?”"
  20,58,"“Rwose natwe tuzakuzanira uburozi bumeze nka bwo; bityo tanga igihe n’ahantu hakwiye ho kuzahurira na we, ku buryo ntawe uzabura muri twese.”"
  20,59,"(Musa) aravuga ati “Tuzahure ku munsi mukuru mwaserutse, kandi (icyo gihe) abantu bazakoranywe ari mu gitondo ku gasusuruko.”"
  20,60,"Nuko Farawo aragenda, maze acura imigambi ye mibisha, nyuma aragaruka (kuri wa munsi mukuru bumvikanye)"
  20,61,Musa arababwira ati “Muramenye mutorama! Ntimuhimbire Allah ikinyoma atavaho akabarimbuza ibihano. Kandi rwose abahimbiye (Allah) ikinyoma bazorama!”
  20,62,"Nuko (abarozi ba Farawo) bajya impaka hagati yabo, bongorerana ku cyo bagomba gukora"
  20,63,"(Abarozi) baravuga bati “Aba bombi (Musa na Haruna) ni abarozi. Umugambi wabo ni uwo kubamenesha mu gihugu cyanyu bakoresheje uburozi bwabo, bakabakura ku myemerere yanyu ntangarugero.”"
  20,64,"(Barabwirana bati) “Ngaho nimwegeranye imigambi yanyu, maze muze ku murongo. Kandi arahiriwe uri butsinde uyu munsi.”"